snippet.title: El Paso, Elsewhere - Official Story Trailer | Summer of Gaming 2023
snippet.description:
Check out this cinematic story trailer for the upcoming retro third-person shooter: El Paso, Elsewhere. This retro shooter is filled with pixelated gunplay, and bullet time slow motion goodness. El Paso, Elsewhere will be available on Xbox Series X/S and Steam in fall of 2023.

#SummerOfGaming #IGN
